<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/15001AMKBTPKPRJBCVBMQKCKPSNVVCTJT> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Majestic Mozart ";
  schema:description """
	CONDUCTOR: Cosette Justo Valdés<span><br/></span>GUEST ARTISTS: Paolo Bortolussi, flute; Hannah Addario-Berry, cello; Lani Krantz, harp; Christopher Lee, clarinet<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join the Vancouver Island Symphony for an exhilarating evening as they unveil the world premiere of Dorothy Chang’s newest VIS commission which showcases the virtuosic playing for our own principal musicians. The program intensifies with Respighi’s ” Trittico Botticelliano,”. Concluding the dynamic lineup is Mozart’s illustrious Symphony No. 41, ensuring a captivating musical experience throughout.<span><br/></span>
""";
